<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA66">
<l>itukaṇṭāy naṉṉeñcē yippiṟavi yāva</l>
<l>titukaṇṭā yellānā muṟṟa – titukaṇṭāy</l>
<l>nāraṇaṉpē rōti narakat tarukaṇaiyāk</l>
<l>kāraṇamum vallaiyēṟ kāṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See this, good heart, this birth’s happening.</l>
<l>See this, all that we’ve undergone. See this, as a reason</l>
<l>not to come close to hell, reciting the names of Nāraṇaṉ.</l>
<l>If you have the strength, look.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
